<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="heart logo">
                <h3>Elderly WeCare</h3></a>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about-us">Who we are</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#how-can-i-help">How can I help?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact-us">Contact Us</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main>
            <section class="main-section">
                <img src="/images/elderly.png" alt="elder woman illustration">
                <div class="text-main-section">
                    <h1>Elderly WeCare</h1>
                    <p>We care about our older people.</p> <p>Please consider donating to us by clicking in the button donate below.</p>
                    <form class="donate-button"><script src="https://checkout.razorpay.com/v1/payment-button.js" data-payment_button_id="pl_Hn171l13mjtApB" async> </script> </form>
                    <!--<button class="donate-button">Donate</button>-->
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="about-us">
                <img src="/images/hands.png" alt="hands touching">
                <div class="about-us-text">
                    <h2>Who we are</h2>

                    <p>Elderly WeCare exists because of our amazing volunteers who selflesly make company and provide help to our elderly community. Thanks to your donation our volunteers can receive a little help with fuel or public transpostation tickets so they can visit our lovely older friends.</p>
